adviseScripts.text: Pit Boss,
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: have you seen Noir?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I fell asleep, and when I woke up, she was gone.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I can't get in touch with her either...
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Maybe she went out on a date.
Maybe she left to practice pole dancing.
Noir? On a date?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: That's impossible.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I have to go find her right away.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Hmm, could be.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Noir has been practicing hard for the performance recently.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I should go check out the practice room.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Wanna go with me?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Blanc and I leave to look for Noir.
Pit Boss,
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: What do you think is the best way for me to transmit happiness?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: By holding hands.
Any method is fine, as long as it brings luck.
Indeed...
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Blanc holds my hand.
I should have known that holding hands was the best method!
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: The best part is that we can do this all day.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Could you... be more specific?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I wanna find the best way to make you happy.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Throughout my entire session with Blanc, I feel elated.
Um... Pit Boss.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Could Noir come with me to our next session?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: It feels kinda lonely when I do it on my own.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Counseling sessions are supposed to be one-on-one.
If that's what you want, go for it.
... I see.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: That's too bad... I think it'd be fun to have Noir join.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Cool, I'll talk to Noir about it!
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: The three of us can hang out afterwards...
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: ... in the Commander's Room.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I have a meaningful session with Blanc.
I think Noir is the prettiest and most beautiful existence in this world.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: What do you think?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: You're awfully pretty yourself, Blanc.
I agree.
Hehe.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Thanks, but I still think Noir is prettier than me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I'm happy that you feel that way, though!
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: You think so too?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I should have known we'd feel the same way about this.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: If only I was half as pretty as Noir...
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I talk to Blanc about Noir.
Sometimes, Rouge gets a bit blue because of her superstitions.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Any idea on how we can help her?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: We can't help someone who can't help themselves.
You should hold her hand.
That makes sense...
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: but surely it'd be easier for her if we lent a hand?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: That's a good idea.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Noir and I are always around Rouge.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Whenever she's feeling down,
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: we'll nuzzle up to her and hold her hand.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: That way, we'll get her out of her funk in no time.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Blac and I talk about ways to help alleviate Rouge's melancholy.
I have a question!
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: What's your favorite type of girl, Pit Boss?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Someone vivacious.
Someone taciturn.
In other words...
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Someone like me!
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Actually, you're my type as well, Pit Boss...
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Oh, so you like quiet girls?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Someone like Noir, then?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Noir is as quiet as they come.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Blanc and I talk about what we look for in a partner.
There are times when we come across rude customers.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: How do you think we should handle them?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Treat them the same way they treat you.
Let me take care of them.
No way!
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: At that the end of the day, they're still our customers.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Don't you have a better suggestion?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Coin Rush's customers can be pretty intimidating. Are you sure you can handle them?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Either way, hearing you say that makes me feel reassured.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Don't worry though, I'll deal with them myself.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Thanks for your concern, Pit Boss.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Blanc and I think about ways to deal with rude customers.
I like Noir so much.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I want to do everything with her.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Even going on a date?
What a great bond you two have.
How did you know?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: As long as neither party has any misgivings, I don't see any problem with it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I'm sure Noir is into the same things that I am.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I'm glad you think so too.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: It's probably because I'm with her every day.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: So, I like the things she likes,
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: and hate the things she doesn't.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I have a meaningful session with Blanc.
Pit Boss, is there any other way I can address you?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Pit Boss sounds so... old-fashioned at times.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Call me by my real name.
Call me "Darling."
{AccountData.NickName}.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Like this?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Ooh, I'm enjoying this!
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: {AccountData.NickName}, make sure to watch my show today!
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: ... Darling.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Hmm... it feels a bit weird to me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: How about I call you by your name instead?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I talk to Blanc about nicknames.
I noticed Alice calls you "Rabbity."
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Would you be willing to try on my bunny ears?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: No thanks.
... Sure, I guess.
Are you sure? I think you'd be adorable in them.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Can't you just try it once?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Really?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: You'll make an adorable bunny, I'm sure of it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Now, which color would suit you best...
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Blanc and I wear bunny ears and hang out for a while.
If I were to wear something aside from the bunny costume,
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: what kind of outfit would be nice?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: You're perfect the way you look now.
A skin-tight dress.
I also think my current looks suit me nicely.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Since you like it too,
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: then I'll stay this way!
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I dunno... tight-fitting clothes aren't the most convenient.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I'd like to try wearing something really fancy for once,
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: but if skin-tight is what interests you, I'll try wearing that next time.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I talk to Blanc about clothes.
Blanc stares at me intently.
Are you in love with me?
... Can you stop staring?
Huh? How did you know?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: You're so handsome, Pit Boss. Not that I'm just now coming to this realization; I've felt this way for a while.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I never get tired of looking at you.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Oh! Sorry.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I didn't realize I was staring.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Blanc and I talk about my appearance.
I've been busy as a bee lately.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: What would you like to do if you had a vacation, Pit Boss?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Hang out with you.
Not budge an inch and have a nice staycation.
So, you like your vacations more on the adventurous side?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Me too.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Next time we both have some time off, we should go somewhere together.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: That's a good way to rest.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Are you sure it wouldn't be too boring, though?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I talk to Blanc about vacations.
I want to make some lucky charms.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: What exactly should I make?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: How about pictures of you?
How about drawings of four-leaf clovers?
Great idea!
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I'll use Noir's pictures too. That way, the luck will be doubled!
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I'll give you one when I'm done.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Hmm...
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I'm not that great at drawing.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Noir can draw pretty well, though. I'll ask her for help.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I talk to Blanc about lucky charms.
I'm going to perform at the theater this weekend.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: You'll come and watch, won't you?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Depends on my schedule that day.
I'll be there, no matter what comes up.
Oh... sounds like you may be busy.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Noir and I worked really hard on this routine though...
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: If it's not convenient, you don't have to come.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Having said that... we did work hard on preparing this performance for you,
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: so it'd be great if you could drop by.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I talk to Blanc about the performance.
One thing on my bucket list is to perform on the surface one day.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: What's something on your bucket list, Pit Boss?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: To perform with you on stage.
To watch your show up on the surface.
You know you can do that now, don't you?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: If you want,
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I can arrange our choreography to include you in the next show.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I can't wait!
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: The stage then will be way bigger than it is now, and there'll be way more people, too.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I hope that day comes sooner rather than later.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I talk to Blanc about bucket lists.
I feel so sad whenever I imagine being away from Noir.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Just last night, I cried thinking about it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: And I hate crying...
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Noir will always be with you.
You shouldn't worry about something that hasn't happened yet.
Thank you for saying that, Pit Boss.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I don't think I could live without Noir.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I value her life more than my own.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I know, but I can't help it sometimes.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Even now, just thinking about it gets me all verklempt.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I try my best to calm down Blanc's overactive imagination.
Pit Boss.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: A or B?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: A.
B.
Good choice!
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: *Kiss*
Blanc gives me a peck on the cheek.
A lucky kiss, for you.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Something wonderful will happen to you today.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Aw shucks, I was thinking of A.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I guess our minds are out of sync today.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I'll still give you one of my drawings as a good luck charm. It's a four-leaf clover!
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I have a particularly lucky counseling session with Blanc.
Pit Boss, is there any chance we can end our session early today?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I've got a date with Noir.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: All right.
Can you bring me with you?
Thanks!
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I haven't decided where we should go.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Can you help me make an itinerary?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Of course!
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Noir will be thrilled.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Where should we go, then?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I spend some time with Blanc thinking about an itinerary.
Yesterday, Noir and I had fun making nicknames for each other.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: If you were to give me a nickname,
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: what would it be?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Good luck bunny.
Hmm... Can you give me some time to think?
That's a nice nickname.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: But I've heard it too many times before.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Can you think of another one?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: Sure, no problem.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I can't tell you how excited I am for you to come up with a unique nickname for me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I wonder what it'll be?
adviseScripts.speaker: Blanc

adviseScripts.text: I spend some time with Blanc brainstorming nicknames.
